806
00:53:15,643 --> 00:53:17,076
Unbelievable.

807
00:53:18,563 --> 00:53:20,155
My God, Sante.

808
00:53:20,363 --> 00:53:21,512
Did you get hit?

809
00:53:21,603 --> 00:53:23,958
Are you kidding?
Thank God we're chickenshits!

810
00:53:24,043 --> 00:53:26,682
Real tough guys would've stood there
and aimed.

811
00:53:27,243 --> 00:53:29,598
