812
00:53:31,843 --> 00:53:34,437
That's Big Mickey from Kansas City.
Friend of ours.

813
00:53:34,643 --> 00:53:36,554
I thought Big Mickey was dead.

814
00:53:37,163 --> 00:53:39,074
The father. This is Little Big Mickey.

815
00:53:39,163 --> 00:53:41,677
Wasn't there a Little Big Mickey
out of Chicago?

816
00:53:41,763 --> 00:53:45,312
That's the original Little Big Mickey.
This is Little Big Mickey Blue Eyes.

817
00:53:45,403 --> 00:53:47,314
So you work for Tony Two-Tone.

818
00:53:50,563 --> 00:53:53,282
Who you got over there?
ls that Sonny Marsalino?

819
00:53:53,363 --> 00:53:54,921
Wasn't he in witness protection?

820
00:53:55,003 --> 00:53:57,756
Took us seven years.
Tracked him and whacked him.

821
00:53:58,563 --> 00:54:00,474
"Tracked him and whacked him."

822
00:54:00,563 --> 00:54:02,281
So who's your guy?

823
00:54:03,323 --> 00:54:04,517
He's a nobody.

824
00:54:04,723 --> 00:54:07,191
Frankie, come on. We showed you ours.

825
00:54:07,363 --> 00:54:09,274
What? We in the second grade?

826
00:54:09,643 --> 00:54:12,282
