-Why?

841
00:54:50,523 --> 00:54:52,718
Get in the car. Don't worry about it.

842
00:54:52,803 --> 00:54:54,919
Look, one thing....

843
00:54:55,723 --> 00:54:57,634
If any of this gets out...

844
00:54:58,243 --> 00:55:00,518
...l'm the one that shot Johnny, okay?

845
00:55:00,963 --> 00:55:02,874
Can we at least agree on that?

846
00:55:04,763 --> 00:55:06,196
You got it.

847
00:55:14,723 --> 00:55:15,997
You all right?

848
00:55:16,563 --> 00:55:18,076
You got my messages?

849
00:55:20,043 --> 00:55:22,557
You buried him and then you dug him up.

850
00:55:23,043 --> 00:55:25,159
And now you don't know where he is.

851
00:55:26,243 --> 00:55:27,517
No, not exactly.

852
00:55:27,603 --> 00:55:29,719
Yeah, I got your messages.

853
00:55:33,323 --> 00:55:34,642
How're you feeling?

854
00:55:36,563 --> 00:55:38,554
Obviously, it's my first murder.

855
00:55:38,843 --> 00:55:42,722
On top of which, I feel like I'm going crazy,
and I'm scared.

856
00:55:42,923 --> 00:55:44,879
And the one person I wanna turn to...

857
00:55:44,963 --> 00:55:47,523
...turns out to be a liar and a fraud.

858
00:55:48,203 --> 00:55:49,272
Other than that--

859
00:55:49,363 --> 00:55:50,557
