863
00:55:58,403 --> 00:55:59,552
Wait.

864
00:56:00,723 --> 00:56:02,236
Hold out your hand.

865
00:56:04,163 --> 00:56:05,278
Here.

866
00:56:05,603 --> 00:56:09,312
Just hang on to it
till I've had a chance to explain.

867
00:56:12,843 --> 00:56:16,597
Come over for lunch tomorrow
and I'll listen to what you have to say.

868
00:56:20,563 --> 00:56:23,441
This is Patrick Richards
reporting from Central Park...

869
00:56:23,523 --> 00:56:27,721
...where police found the body
of 31-year-old Jonathan Graziosi...

870
00:56:27,923 --> 00:56:30,721
...son of reputed Mob boss Vito Graziosi.

871
00:56:31,403 --> 00:56:35,840
Sources tell us the body was found
with a rolled-up $100 bill in one nostril...

872
00:56:36,003 --> 00:56:39,200
...calling card of the notorious
Risolli crime family.

873
00:56:39,363 --> 00:56:42,435
Johnny was at the beginning
of a flourishing art career.

874
00:57:07,923 --> 00:57:11,313
Tony Risolli called. They wanna talk.

875
00:57:12,523 --> 00:57:14,514
Okay. Set it up.

876
00:57:19,203 --> 00:57:22,001
As soon as they pull up,
we should blow them away.

877
00:57:24,563 --> 00:57:26,793
Let's listen to what they got to say.

878
00:57:48,883 --> 00:57:52,637
Mr. Risolli says he swears
on the soul of his mother...

879
00:57:52,843 --> 00:57:54,913
...he had nothing to do with this.

880
00:57:55,043 --> 00:57:56,158
Then who?

881
00:58:02,923 --> 00:58:05,039
A cop in the 20th precinct tipped us.

882
00:58:05,123 --> 00:58:09,116
They towed Johnny's car from a building
on the Upper West Side.

883
00:58:10,003 --> 00:58:11,675
That's the address.

884
00:58:14,723 --> 00:58:15,678
Go.

885
00:58:16,803 --> 00:58:17,918
No, wait.

886
00:58:20,403 --> 00:58:24,840
You don't want everyone stomping around
up there, scaring people away.

887
00:58:26,123 --> 00:58:28,842
How about I go in there
with a detective's badge?

888
00:58:28,923 --> 00:58:31,232
You know, ask around. Keep it quiet.

889
00:58:31,963 --> 00:58:34,796
We find the right zebra,
we tear him to pieces.

890
00:58:52,003 --> 00:58:53,880
Tickle my tummy!

891
00:59:11,363 --> 00:59:14,673
Which apartment was the old lady in
that saw us with Johnny?

892
00:59:15,043 --> 00:59:16,158
Why?

893
00:59:18,443 --> 00:59:20,001
