894
00:59:20,483 --> 00:59:22,917
We need to talk to her about it.

895
00:59:31,123 --> 00:59:33,034
What's that? What are you gonna do?

896
00:59:33,123 --> 00:59:35,193
Please. I am not gonna hurt her.

897
00:59:35,363 --> 00:59:36,591
-No, Listen--
-You can't--

898
00:59:36,683 --> 00:59:39,436
