-Who is it?

899
00:59:39,803 --> 00:59:42,397
Michael Felgate
and his harmless friend Frank.

900
00:59:42,523 --> 00:59:44,320
Mrs. Horton, do not open--

901
00:59:44,523 --> 00:59:45,319
What?

902
00:59:45,443 --> 00:59:48,003
Mrs. Horton, he said,
"Please open the door."

903
00:59:48,123 --> 00:59:51,160
You're Michael's friend?
The garbage helper?

904
00:59:51,483 --> 00:59:53,280
Yes, the garbage helper.

905
00:59:53,883 --> 00:59:55,282
Would you stop it?

906
01:00:04,323 --> 01:00:06,200
What are you guys doing here?

907
01:00:06,403 --> 01:00:08,963
Mr. Risolli thought we should check it out.

908
01:00:10,203 --> 01:00:11,795
Hey, Mickey Blue!

909
01:00:13,083 --> 01:00:14,562
Thank you very much.

910
01:00:14,683 --> 01:00:17,595
If you remember anything else,
call that number.

911
01:00:19,803 --> 01:00:23,000
We covered this place,
but most of the people are at work.

912
01:00:23,203 --> 01:00:27,162
How about we grab some steak,
we all come back later this afternoon?

913
01:00:27,363 --> 01:00:29,752
We look like we ever said no to a steak?

914
01:00:29,963 --> 01:00:31,715
And I got the perfect place.

915
01:00:31,803 --> 01:00:32,997
You'll love it, Frank.

916
01:00:33,083 --> 01:00:34,436
Follow us.

917
01:00:45,323 --> 01:00:46,995
Hey. Forget about it!

918
01:00:47,243 --> 01:00:49,154
"Hey. Forget about it."

919
01:00:49,883 --> 01:00:52,033
"Forget about it." No R's.

920
01:00:52,323 --> 01:00:53,836
"Forget about it."

921
01:00:54,043 --> 01:00:55,715
Now change the T's to D's.

922
01:00:55,803 --> 01:00:57,395
"Forget about it."

923
01:00:57,803 --> 01:00:58,713
"ld"?

924
01:00:58,923 --> 01:01:00,914
You said change the T's to D's!

925
01:01:01,123 --> 01:01:02,442
Not the last one.

926
01:01:02,523 --> 01:01:04,514
Change them, but not the last one.

927
01:01:04,603 --> 01:01:06,116
Wait, forget about it.

928
01:01:06,203 --> 01:01:07,079
Stop.

929
01:01:07,203 --> 01:01:08,602
Try this one here:

930
01:01:09,403 --> 01:01:10,995
"Get the hell outta here." No Rs.

931
01:01:11,083 --> 01:01:13,119
"Get the hell outta here."

932
01:01:13,323 --> 01:01:14,676
